ygData.messageBody:
Does anyone have the loc for Tib? I'm level 26, and heard this wasn't the
best place to solo (unkempt druids), but the two treants and the aviak city
are sooooo over camped on my server. Even at 4 in the morning when only 550
are on the server, at least 65 are in S. Karana. If anyone has better ideas
of what to solo at this level, I'd be very interested in hearing from you. I
really don't like the idea of wandering mobs sneaking up on me - but its
better than waiting 2 hours for a damn aviak....

-- Darnizhaan D'Mortis
